{ This is the most logical move. I tried other moves, but they don't offer enough. }
10. Qc2 { This is the other possibility, and now the fun really starts ! }
10... Nb4 11. Qb1 O-O-O
{ I really like to make this move when it's good ! It feels as though you can do everything ! }
12. a3 Rd1+
{ What a pleasure it is to make such a move. Simply an amazing resource. } 13.
Nxd1 Nc2+ 14. Qxc2 Qxc2 15. Bf4 Qf5 16. Rc1+ Kd7
{ Black's king is in the center, but it is difficult for White to create winning threats. Black will play ...Bd6 followed by ...Rc8 and the position will be more or less equal. }
