d5
{ I like this the most.   3...d6  4.Be2  Nf6  5.Nc3  g6  6.h4 !?  White has some compensation. }
4. Be2 { 4.exd5  Qxd5  5.Nf3  g6  6.Nc3  Qe6+  7.Be2  Bg7  =+ } 4... Nf6 5.
exd5 { 5.e5  Nfd7  6.Nf3  e6  Black has the best French ever !! } 5... Qxd5 6.
Nf3 Bg4
{ Yes, it's not the Scandinavian since White is missing something on g2 ! } *

