{ Black needs to continue playing with his initiative. What is the best move? }
1... Qf6
{ Yes, he played the best move in the game !   17...Bc6  18.Nd4 !  The knight on d4 will defend everything.   17...h5 ?!  This is too slow.  18.Rad1  Nxf3+  19.Bxf3  h4  20.Qe4 !  Once again, the queen in the center means that there is no mate ! }
