{ White is under a lot of pressure. ...Bxc3 is a threat. What to do now ? } 1.
Rad1
{ I have hopefully already successfully taught you how to think in this kind of situation. If you have learnt that fast, I'm proud of you ! }
1... Bxc3
{ 19...Nxh2 !  This is the best chance.  20.Kxh2  Qh4+  21.Kg1  Bxg3  22.fxg3  Qxg3+  23.Kh1  Qh3+  24.Kg1  and Black should give perpetual. }
2. Rxd7 Bxb2 3. Rxd8+ Rxd8 4. Bxg4 Bxa3 5. Qa4 Qb2 6. Qxa7 Qxb4 7. Bf3
{ The position is a draw, but Black should still suffer a little bit longer. }
